She had successfuly replicated the baby spider.  Then she took it and 
put it in the DNA analyzer and sorted out the DNA.  She then put the 
information and the DNA sample and put it into the replicator.   She 
waited to see if she could make one of Phobia's babies.  Is so, then 
she could try to find something with Phobia's DNA and bring him back. 
Well, sort of.
